{"tid":1637570,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］ 五大訴求同解散警隊前要準備既措施","createTime":"2019-10-08T04:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T06:48:23.000Z","uid":148403,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0fcd008285f74395ea5badd8caa4e9494b10ed43","tid":1637570,"uid":148403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:33:44.000Z","msg":"當我地成功解散警隊既時候等於香港冇執法機關，如果有黑社會拎槍械出黎打劫，甘就冇人制止到佢地，宜家係咪要諗埋五大訴求加解散警隊之後既彌補？<br />\n<br />\n有聽過用海關、廉政公署、懲教署補上警隊既事務，但係有冇諗過佢地識唔識做、有冇人做，同埋以上既行業就會小左人。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我地革命尚未成功，但係都要諗諗我地真係拉倒左政府、警隊時，香港就會出現左無政府狀態，甘會好危險。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"5cb3d6f0d4a83da4f754e1d8368a5635d87eb021","tid":1637570,"uid":148403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:34:17.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e3aa03db8eac89900bd9cde9c20940a4c2ea314f","tid":1637570,"uid":148403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"ec7b5244d8535f4852841bc288627212cb4a4292","tid":1637570,"uid":148403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"75af7aa7d2173b3e3f427051cf031163a7c097c1","tid":1637570,"uid":148403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"c69c3f37311cb85bea9e861d8f4a552f0c95b6a5","tid":1637570,"uid":148403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:35:06.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"1d4d2122e75c55b03514f4d1201217bd6cb821c9","tid":1637570,"uid":148403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"757f407af021ef389441bf92832bdc60cce3b5bd","tid":1637570,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"試吓開時事台"},{"pid":"d6b3bea320fc84a4806f78e87adb6e7b0311feea","tid":1637570,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc